'''Pyre Folas''' was a major city on the planet of [[Teyr/Legends|Teyr]], on the south face of the [[Teyr Rift]]. The [[Rift Skyrail]] ran between the city and [[Turos Noth]] to the west. Pyre Folas was considered the welcome center to the planet. It hosted the [[Mobquet Presents: Fastest Land Beings]] race.

